title: Rand Paul still live streaming, still running for president
text: Rand Paul still live streaming, still running for president Wednesday, 14 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) Quotes of the day from the 2016 presidential candidates - said on the campaign trail, Oct. 14, 2015 More Rand Paul Than You Ever Thought Possible 00:44 Rand Paul is going to give voters a glimpse into the hectic life of a presidential candidate on the campaign trail. The Republican presidential hopeful says he plans to live stream an entire day on the campaign trail in Iowa where he is currently campaigning. Paul spokesman Sergio Gor told Mashable...
